com.imkrisna.samsung.nservice

Class NSListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.imkrisna.samsung.nservice.NSListener

  • public abstract class NSListener
extends Activity

    This class extending android Activity class. To use this library, the common android class which extending Activity class should replaced with extending NSListener class. The workflow of application will not significantly changed since NSListener class also extending Activity.

    NSListener provide abstract function or interface for another class in library to access/call the android main class which enable android to discover, connect, and communicate with N-Service capable devices like Samsung Smart TV, BD Player and Home-Theather seamlessly.

    Version:
    1.0.1
    Author:
    I Made Krisna Widhiastra (im.krisna@gmail.com)
